message.entry: The argument must be a character vector.
The argument must be 'help' when providing only 1 argument.
Can not provide both the argument 'sourceFile' and the argument 'sourceText'.
Must provide a pair of character vectors (msgId, msgTxt) for the translated messages argument.
The argument 'msgs' must be a [Nx2] cell array of character vectors.
Must provide 'sourceFile' or 'sourceText'. Call codeinstrum.internal.codecov.report.code2html('help') for a complete description.
The input source file name is the same as the output HTML file name.
